  },
  {
    name: '2D Game Engine',
    technologies: ['Java'],
    description: '**Game engine** designed to make creating 2D Java games simple. Engine manages **resolution scaling**, **delta timing**, **double buffer rendering**, and provides an intuitive **API** to get started.',
